### LifeLog API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ===== Authentication =====

### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "username": "johndoe",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "display_name": "John Doe"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!"
}

### Login with TOTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "totp_code": "123456"
}

### Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh_token": "{{refresh_token}}"
}

### Verify Email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{verification_token}}"
}

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com"
}

### Reset Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{reset_token}}",
  "password": "NewSecurePass456!"
}

### Setup TOTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/totp/setup
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Verify TOTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/totp/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "code": "123456"
}

### Disable TOTP
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/totp/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Passkey Registration (WebAuthn)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/passkey/register
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Passkey Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/passkey/login
Content-Type: application/json

### List Sessions
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Revoke Session
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/sessions/{{session_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Revoke All Sessions
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ===== Users =====

### Get Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Profile
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "display_name": "John Updated",
  "bio": "Life logger enthusiast"
}

### Get Settings
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/settings
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Settings
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/settings
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "theme": "dark",
  "language": "en",
  "notification_enabled": true,
  "daily_reminder_time": "20:00"
}

### List Notifications
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications?page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Mark Notification Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications/{{notification_id}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Mark All Notifications Read
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me/notifications/read
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ===== Entries =====

### List Entries
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries?page=1&page_size=20&sort=entry_date&sort_dir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Entries with Filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries?entry_type=mood&mood_min=5&start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-06-09&search=good
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Entry
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "entry_type": "mood",
  "title": "Great day!",
  "description": "Had a wonderful day",
  "mood_score": 8,
  "activities": ["reading", "exercise", "cooking"],
  "visibility": "private",
  "entry_date": "2026-06-09"
}

### Create Journal Entry
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "entry_type": "journal",
  "title": "Reflections",
  "markdown_content": "# Today\n\nIt was a **productive** day.\n\n- Finished the project\n- Went for a walk\n\n> Stay focused!",
  "visibility": "private",
  "entry_date": "2026-06-09"
}

### Get Entry
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/{{entry_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Entry
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/{{entry_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "mood_score": 9
}

### Delete Entry
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/{{entry_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### List Tags
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Tag
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/tags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "important",
  "color": "#EF4444"
}

### Delete Tag
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/entries/tags/{{tag_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ===== Habits =====

### List Habits
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Habit
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "Read for 30 minutes",
  "description": "Read books daily",
  "habit_type": "daily",
  "frequency": 1,
  "color": "#10B981"
}

### Get Habit
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/{{habit_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Habit
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/{{habit_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "name": "Read for 1 hour",
  "frequency": 1
}

### Delete Habit
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/{{habit_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Log Habit Completion
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/{{habit_id}}/log
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "value": 1,
  "note": "Finished chapter 5"
}

### Get Habit Logs
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/{{habit_id}}/logs?start_date=2026-01-01&end_date=2026-06-09
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Habit Stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Habit Heatmap
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/habits/heatmap?year=2026
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### ===== Goals =====

### List Goals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals?page=1&page_size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Goal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Read 50 books",
  "description": "Read 50 books this year",
  "goal_type": "yearly",
  "target_value": 50,
  "unit": "books",
  "start_date": "2026-01-01",
  "end_date": "2026-12-31"
}

### Get Goal
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Update Goal
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Read 60 books",
  "target_value": 60
}

### Delete Goal
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Add Goal Progress
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}/progress
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "value": 1,
  "note": "Finished 'The Great Gatsby'"
}

### Get Goal Progress
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Goal Milestones
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}/milestones
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Milestone
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/{{goal_id}}/milestones
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "title": "Halfway there!",
  "target_value": 25
}

### Delete Milestone
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/milestones/{{milestone_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Goal Stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/goals/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

