### ===== MQTT =====

### Publish MQTT Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/mqtt/publish
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "topic": "life/entry/create",
  "payload": {
    "type": "mood",
    "value": 7,
    "activities": ["reading"],
    "note": "Published via MQTT"
  }
}

